interpretation:
The last quarter moon emoji represents a time of transition and reflection. It signals the end of a cycle and the beginning of a new one. This card asks you to look back at the past and reflect on what you have learned. It may be time to let go of old habits, relationships, or patterns that no longer serve you. The last quarter moon reminds you that change is necessary for growth and encourages you to embrace it. 

Overall, the last quarter moon emoji represents a powerful moment of transformation and evolution. It invites you to embrace change and trust the journey ahead.
